{
  "stem": "268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And of course, having [YIDDISH] and smoked all kind of [INAUDIBLE], really wonderful appetizers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And main dishes, borscht, chicken soup, oh, wow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Chicken soup, her chicken soup I could probably patent and could market it well here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It's of course true for a lot of Jewish mothers, not only mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Everyone would say, Mama, this chicken soup was the best.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the aroma, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on in life, I kept thinking about the aroma when you walked in the kitchen, especially on a Friday, Friday afternoon, preparing for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The aroma of a fresh-baked Challah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the chicken soup would, you know, I would smell it walking up the stairs in the hallway.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Gentile neighbors would always be, in a way, envious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because she would bake and cook for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our Gentile neighbors would make a big deal out of baking a cake.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would spend a lot of money buying-- sometimes they would-- my dad used to say they would go and ask for advanced pay, because they got to bake for this big holiday, either Christmas or Easter, or certain the saints which they observed-- this was Catholic country-- and so they would bake big pans, you know, maybe three by four-foot pan, big cakes.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother used to bake a nice cake, a round or rectangular cake for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would say, how can you bake every week?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can you have cake every week?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess my mom knew how to budget better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was my mom, the cook.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Any memories come to mind of Jewish holidays when you were a child?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, the major ones-- Passover, Shavuot, and high holidays-- Rosh Hashanah, Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Passover.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I like Passover.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I like the story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I like the Seder.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
